com.sun.jna

Class ELFAnalyser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jna.ELFAnalyser

  • class ELFAnalyser
extends Object
    Analyse an ELF file for platform specific attributes.

    Primary use-case: Detect whether the java binary is arm hardfloat or softfloat.
